ntic alignment filtering in real data branch and style transfer construction\", \"bib_key\": \"\", \"source\": \"llm\"}, {\"paper_id\": \"\", \"title\": \"ZETA\", \"cite_type\": \"supported_by\", \"context\": \"Used to convert target audio to new style while preserving temporal structure and pitch\", \"bib_key\": \"\", \"source\": \"llm\"}, {\"paper_id\": \"\", \"title\": \"Scaper\", \"cite_type\": \"supported_by\", \"context\": \"Toolkit used for programmatic soundscape generation in the synthetic data branch\", \"bib_key\": \"\", \"source\": \"llm\"}, {\"paper_id\": \"\", \"title\": \"VGGSound\", \"cite_type\": \"supported_by\", \"context\": \"Real-world audio dataset used as input for the AudioEdit dataset construction engine\", \"bib_key\": \"\", \"source\": \"llm\"}, {\"paper_id\": \"\", \"title\": \"ESC-50\", \"cite_type\": \"supported_by\", \"context\": \"Foreground sound dataset used for synthetic data generation in AudioEdit\", \"bib_key\": \"\", \"source\": \"llm\"}, {\"paper_id\": \"\", \"title\": \"AudioCaps\", \"cite_type\": \"supported_by\", \"context\": \"Background audio dataset used for synthetic data generation in AudioEdit and as T2A generation benchmark\", \"bib_key\": \"\", \"source\": \"llm\"}, {\"paper_id\": \"\", \"title\": \"Synchformer\", \"cite_type\": \"supported_by\", \"context\": \"Pretrained model used to extract video synchronization features at 25fps\", \"bib_key\": \"\", \"source\": \"llm\"}, {\"paper_id\": \"\", \"title\": \"ConvNeXtV2\", \"cite_type\": \"supported_by\", \"context\": \"Architecture used for the transcription encoder (4 blocks) in the generation module\", \"bib_key\": \"\", \"source\": \"llm\"}, {\"paper_id\": \"\", \"title\": \"MMSU\", \"cite_type\": \"eval_by\", \"context\": \"Understanding benchmark with 47 spoken language tasks\", \"bib_key\": \"\", \"source\": \"llm\"}, {\"paper_id\": \"\", \"title\": \"MMAU\", \"cite_type\": \"eval_by\", \"context\": \"Understanding benchmark across 27 reasoning skills in soun